item.title: Unresponding program
item.dc:creator: @runescape3dude runescape3dude
item.description:
@runescape3dude wrote:

[quote=“Kane., post:5, topic:244177”][quote author=thefalloffuckingtroy. link=topic=320547.msg2537401#msg2537401 date=1226814524]

Save your work every 5 minutes?

You can do that?

no i can’t.
[/quote]
Well, now you can’t, 'cause it’s unresponsive. But you should have saved it every 5 minutes to avoid losing all your work.

Good one.[/quote]
At some stages I saved my work after ever second word/sentence. (School can be a bad place to do laptop work)
